            "title": "法國和日本的船隻通過霍爾木茲海峽 或為伊朗戰爭爆發後首次",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><div class=\"relative mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"relative mb-1 overflow-hidden rounded-lg lg:mb-2\"><div class=\"flex transition-transform duration-300 ease-in-out\"><div class=\"aspect-[3/2] w-full shrink-0 grow-0 basis-full\"><div class=\"absolute -z-1 h-full w-full bg-cover bg-center blur-[var(--text-px20)]\" style=\"background-image:url(https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/uLEceUSUyTlD3TLpUmYFaw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTcyOA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/44b006926e6f0275db300a2d98438f40)\"></div><img alt=\"一艘法國所有的貨櫃船駛出霍爾木茲海峽\" class=\"h-full w-full bg-black/30 object-contain\" height=\"728\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/uLEceUSUyTlD3TLpUmYFaw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTcyOA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/44b006926e6f0275db300a2d98438f40\" width=\"960\"/></div><div class=\"aspect-[3/2] w-full shrink-0 grow-0 basis-full\"><div class=\"absolute -z-1 h-full w-full bg-cover bg-center blur-[var(--text-px20)]\" style=\"background-image:url(https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/NId0esw66xRrAdPOcx03NQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTcyOA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/564a6c41d8c60348872b8813ae79a0ea)\"></div><img alt=\"一艘法國所有的貨櫃船駛出霍爾木茲海峽\" class=\"h-full w-full bg-black/30 object-contain\" height=\"728\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/NId0esw66xRrAdPOcx03NQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTcyOA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/564a6c41d8c60348872b8813ae79a0ea\" width=\"960\"/></div></div><button class=\"border-dirty-seagull bg-main-level-1 lg:bg-main-level-1/75 hover:bg-main-level-1 text-slide-arrow absolute top-1/2 flex h-10 w-10 -translate-y-1/2 cursor-pointer items-center justify-center rounded-full border left-[8px] lg:left-[24px]\" data-testid=\"prev-button\" data-ylk=\"ct:slideshow;elm:arrow;itc:1;sec:sshow;slk:prev;\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class