        {
            "title": "中東最大鋁生產商的工廠遭襲受損嚴重 全面復產或需一年",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 中東最大鋁生產商阿聯酋環球鋁業表示，在不久前遭伊朗襲擊後，其位於阿布達比的工廠可能需要長達一年時間才能恢復全面生產。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">阿聯酋環球鋁業表示，Al Taweelah冶煉廠在遭受飛彈和無人機的重大破壞後進入緊急停產狀態。該公司周五在聲明中表示已完成對設施的初步損失評估，並在與貨運可能受到影響的客戶聯繫。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">中東地區約占全球鋁產量的9%，但由於其他地區產量受限影響了庫存，使市場幾乎沒有緩衝空間來應對沖擊，戰爭的影響被放大。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-b72ea070-301c-32ab-b22d-a5d295d4faab-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「要恢復冶煉廠運營，必須修復受損的基礎設施，並逐步恢復每一個電解槽，」該公司在聲明中表示。「初步跡象表明，完全恢復原鋁生產可能需要長達12個月。」</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">自伊朗戰爭爆發以來，倫敦金屬交易所的鋁價已上漲逾10%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Top UAE Aluminum Firm May Take Year to Restore Full Output (1)</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Julian Luk.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"bloomberg.com\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%B8%AD%E6%9D%B1%E6%9C%80%E5%A4%A7%E9%8B%81%E7%94%9F%E7%94%A2%E5%95%86%E7%9A%84%E5%B7%A5%E5%BB%A0%E9%81%AD%E8%A5%B2%E5%8F%97%E6%90%8D%E5%9A%B4%E9%87%8D-%E5%85%A8%E9%9D%A2%E5%BE%A9%E7%94%A2%E6%88%96%E9%9C%80-%E5%B9%B4-173530499.html",
